    <AbstractNarration>The proposed study will protect 2 discrete areas of marsh with 200 plastic&lt;br/&gt;barrier film isolation units (In Situ Isolation Systems - ISIS) as oil encroaches the area. The&lt;br/&gt;isolated areas will be studied for protection from oil and plant health for up to 2 weeks before&lt;br/&gt;onset of contamination and 6 weeks after. If effective, rapid scale up to larger areas of marsh is&lt;br/&gt;proposed. Industry collaborations to enable further scale up have been defined.</AbstractNarration>
